<h3 .text-white>Privacy Policy (GDPR)

<p .text-white>
    We don't directly store any data about you however elements embedded from external sources
    such as YouTube videos may track you according to their privacy policies.

$if loggedIn
    <p .text-white>
        Logging into the site uses Google OAuth which involves Google providing us with a token
        after you login with your Google account. This token is then stored in our database.
        We do not have access to your Google account password. If you would like us to remove
        your token then click the button below.

    <button #forgetButton .btn .btn-primary >Forget Me!